scene.message:
Yukino: What the heck?!{nl}
This chest?{waitkey}{clearbox}Is she making fun{nl}
of us?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: This is Michiko we're{nl}
talking about. She'd pull{nl}
something this pointless{waitkey}{clearbox}and snide. Still... the path{nl}
from the torture room to this{nl}
room... was grueling...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Is this the chest with{nl}
the "Mirror Shard" that{nl}
Michiko mentioned?{waitkey}{clearbox}Still... the path from the{nl}
torture room to this room...{nl}
was Very hard...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ugh, I'm dying!{nl}
I don't wanna move!{nl}
Whose idea was this?{waitkey}{clearbox}Who said "let's go get{nl}
the Mirror Shard"??{waitkey}{clearbox}If that shard's not in this{nl}
box, Ayase and friends are{nl}
worn out for nothing!{waitkey}Boo! Boooo!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Still, it's a clearly{nl}
suspicious-looking chest.{nl}
Who'll open it?{waitkey}{clearbox}The odds of a trap{nl}
are enormous.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Doesn't this thing{nl}
reek of a trap? Any way{nl}
you look at it?{waitkey}{clearbox}Who's gonna open it?{nl}
I'm the introverted type,{nl}
not the sort to stand{waitkey}out front, so I'll pass.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: No time limit or not,{nl}
we've taken a bit{nl}
too long.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: I'm done!!{nl}
I'm tired!{nl}
I'm resting!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Even I am fed up{nl}
with this tower's{nl}
nastiness.{waitkey}{clearbox}It's just like Michiko's{nl}
very character.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Fugah!{nl}
I'm beat!{waitkey}{clearbox}Thinking we gotta go all{nl}
the way back to that torture{nl}
room gives me the chills!{waitkey}{ret}

Obtained a "Mirror Shard"!{waitkey}{clearbox}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{nl}
There's something like{nl}
a paper in the corner{nl}
of the box.{waitkey}{clearbox}...A letter from Michiko,{nl}
it seems.{waitkey}{clearbox}You opened the letter.{waitkey}{ret}

"Ohohohohoho! To actually{nl}
reach this chest - what{nl}
greedy people you are!{waitkey}{clearbox}It must have been quite the{nl}
ordeal. Ohohohohoho!{nl}
Well? Was what you sought{waitkey}inside?{waitkey}{clearbox}Unlike you humans, I{nl}
don't tell lies!{waitkey}{clearbox}So as promised, I'll tell you{nl}
Michiko's weakness, clear{nl}
as can be!{waitkey}{clearbox}I-{wait_fr:30}t-{wait_fr:30}'s-{wait_fr:30} this♥{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Don't take too much time!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ohohohoho! Hurry to me!{nl}
I'll be waiting, dearie♥{waitkey}{clearbox}Well? Was that helpful?{nl}
Now then, good day."{nl}
    From Michiko{waitkey}     For You{waitkey}{ret}
